        <solution id="solfhsst_id1022"> <list id="listfhsst_id1022" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic" class="stepwise">
        <item> <label> Check what you have and the units </label>
        <para id="id65595">We have a circuit with a battery and three resistors. We know the voltage across the battery and two of the resistors. We want to find that voltage across the unknown resistor.</para>
